      "description": "This vehicle is a breathtaking time capsule, meticulously preserved to satisfy the most demanding collector. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple and matte with no bolster wear, and the interior still retains its original showroom scent. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or snow. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history documenting oil changes every 3,000 miles and proactive preventative maintenance. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Included are all original keys, the window sticker, and a custom car cover.",
